{"title":"茶境（组诗）","authors":["李汉荣"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":7,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"茶境（组诗）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李汉荣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远　方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔着透明的玻璃，我听见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远山浅绿的歌唱；一些芽尖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一些遥远的细节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经不住热情的询问"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渐渐浮出记忆的水面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见茶树，这多情的灌木"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被风推搡着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又被月光扶起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一声声鸟的问候里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吐露心事；云雾漫过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年的伤口附近，长出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"温柔的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见采茶的妹妹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在云岭上站着，移动着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满手的白云和绿叶，一片片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是心中刚刚发芽的对爱的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想象"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔着茶杯，我听见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她细细的叮咛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在渐渐淡去的时光里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心，沉入更深的水域"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仪　式"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每次饮茶，我都要用清水洗手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对茶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如同面对一位"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我爱慕的纯真女子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我交给她的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只能是干净的手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干净的心情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每次饮茶，我都要用清水洗手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手啊，很多时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不得不"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忍受不洁和污浊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以及硬物的伤害"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在茶的气息里放松吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看捧着绿叶的手，多么可爱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每次饮茶，我都用清水洗手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是习惯，也是一种心灵仪式"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对一杯茶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个国家，一个星球"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有干净的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才知道小心地捧起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每次饮茶，我都要用清水洗手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在被茶接受之前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我得首先清洁自己"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一尘不染的茶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这绿色的仙药"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进入凡尘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未必能医好所有的病"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但至少带给我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"次次洗手的机会"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}